events.1848: Dodoma becomes an Arab caravan town
events.1907: Dodoma becomes a German garrison town
events.1913: Dodoma designated the capital of the German colony of Tanganyika
events.1920: German colonial rule ends after World War I; Dodoma becomes part of British Tanganyika
events.1961: Dodoma officially designated the capital of Tanganyika upon independence from British colonial rule
events.1967: Dodoma retains its capital status when Tanganyika merges with Zanzibar to form Tanzania
events.2018: Tanzanian government announces plans to move all government functions to Dodoma from Dar es Salaam
